text: St. Patrick's Day Slam (2021) was a professional wrestling show made by All Elite Wrestling (AEW). It took place on March 10, 2021 at the Daily's Place in Jacksonville, Florida. The event aired as special episode of Dynamite. It was the first St. Patrick's Day Slam event held by AEW. The main event of the show saw Thunder Rosa defeated Dr. Britt Baker, D.M.D. in a Unsanctioned Lights Out match. Rosa hit Baker with a Fire Thunder Driver through the table to get the victory.
